content: Sensitivity tests are used in automotive, aerospace, mining, and other fields. They are also used to test the the effectiveness and maximum permissible safe level of drugs, medicines, and pesticides. In biological fields, sensitivity tests are also called LD50 or LC50 tests.

description: Data file created with SenTest, a scientific application used for sensitivity testing and data analysis; contains the results of tests conducted with sensitivity recording equipment.
